<c74object name='sp.playbackcore~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>A <o>poly~</o> for corpus sample playback</digest>
    <description>A <o>poly~</o> for corpus sample playback.</description>
    <discussion>    <h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
    <p>The <o>sp.playbackcore~</o> object is the underlying <o>poly~</o> that handles the polyphonic sample playback of matched corpus entries. It's not intended to be used on its own, but rather is the core component of <o>sp.corpusplayer~</o>.</p>
</discussion>

